1
00:00:55,160 --> 00:00:56,480
Heavenly Emperor.

2
00:00:56,840 --> 00:01:00,770
You've practiced forbidden arts for years, yet you haven't improved.

3
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:03,480
No wonder you need Aran to protect you,

4
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:05,770
and your so-called common people.

5
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:07,210
Who exactly are you?

6
00:01:08,039 --> 00:01:09,900
You were no match for me back then.

7
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:11,440
And now,

8
00:01:12,080 --> 00:01:14,240
you still can't defeat me.

9
00:01:17,320 --> 00:01:18,120
It's you.

10
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:28,480
Huoyeyan.

11
00:01:33,160 --> 00:01:36,479
Practicing forbidden arts leads to madness.

12
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:42,440
I was kind enough to warn you,

13
00:01:42,960 --> 00:01:44,960
yet you repay kindness with enmity.

14
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:47,560
You know too much.

15
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:55,680
I failed to kill you back then.

16
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:02,120
Today is the day you die.

17
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,320
Ayin.

18
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:12,400
Aran.

19
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:14,850
Senior Brother.

20
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:15,840
Aran.

21
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:18,200
No!

22
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:27,320
Aran.

23
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:28,720
Aran.

24
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:32,560
I saved you again.

25
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,480
My Lord,

26
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:48,040
it's no use.

27
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:50,960
Promise me.

28
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,720
No more war.

29
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:56,200
Do not hurt the innocent.

30
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:59,880
Aran, don't speak.

31
00:03:00,760 --> 00:03:02,000
Save your strength.

32
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:04,480
We haven't married yet.

33
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:07,290
You haven't become my Empress yet.

34
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,160
You can't die.

35
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:13,680
Didn't we agree to protect the world together?

36
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,760
If you die,

37
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:18,760
I will destroy this world

38
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:20,280
to bury it with you.

39
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:24,000
Ayin.

40
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:26,680
I think I understand

41
00:03:28,079 --> 00:03:29,480
what love is now.

42
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,280
Aran.

43
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:35,120
Don't waste your energy.

44
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:37,240
My time has come.

45
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:39,840
Promise me.

46
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,760
Live for me.

47
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,280
Live well.

48
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,420
Protect the world.

49
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:50,360
I searched for you for a thousand years.

50
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:53,600
I won't let you leave me again.

51
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:58,800
I only just realized my own heart.

52
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:03,680
It's too late to be your Empress.

53
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:09,770
Senior Brother.

54
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:13,930
Senior Brother.

55
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,279
I'm sorry.

56
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:19,490
I'm the one who wronged you.

57
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:21,760
I'm the one who failed Aran.

58
00:04:22,280 --> 00:04:23,280
Promise me.

59
00:04:23,640 --> 00:04:27,760
Keep the world at peace.

60
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:33,640
Okay.

61
00:04:34,520 --> 00:04:35,800
I promise you.

62
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:38,440
Peace for the world.

63
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:49,000
Ayin.

64
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:50,920
Aran.

65
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:09,200
Aran.

66
00:05:09,640 --> 00:05:10,560
Aran.

67
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:14,460
I hope I'm not too late.

68
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:16,440
However,

69
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:20,000
even if this forbidden technique saves the Goddess,

70
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:22,080
she won't be herself anymore.

71
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:28,760
My Lord.

72
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,480
For this day,

73
00:05:36,159 --> 00:05:38,600
I have waited ten thousand years.

74
00:05:39,280 --> 00:05:40,080
My Lord.

75
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:42,290
Pardon my boldness.

76
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:43,680
Rumor has it,

77
00:05:43,840 --> 00:05:45,480
he who holds the Spirit Pearl commands the Dragon Clan.

78
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:47,840
And he who commands the Dragon Clan rules the world.

79
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:49,240
You already control the Dragon Clan.

80
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:52,240
Why do you still need the Seven-Colored Divine Stone?

81
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:55,159
The Spirit Pearl, such an ancient spiritual artifact,

82
00:05:55,159 --> 00:05:59,040
has always been beyond the reach of our Demon Clan.

83
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:03,280
Only when it is refined into the Seven-Colored Divine Stone

84
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,920
can it be used by me.

85
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:08,280
Once I obtain the Seven-Colored Divine Stone,

86
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:09,940
I can reshape my physical body

87
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:12,600
and transform into a supreme spiritual form.

88
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,800
When that time comes,

89
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:16,520
I will rewrite the laws of heaven and earth.

90
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:20,240
I will make the Three Realms live according to my will.

91
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:23,040
May Your Highness achieve your wish soon

92
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:26,090
and lead our Demon Clan to unify the Three Realms.

93
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:28,840
Gather the elite of the Demon Clan.

94
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:32,000
Go with me to seize the Seven-Colored Divine Stone.

95
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:35,640
The future of our Demon Clan depends on this battle.

96
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:38,840
As you command.

97
00:06:54,520 --> 00:06:55,480
Yunyuan.

98
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:57,640
Ling'er.

99
00:06:58,159 --> 00:06:59,000
You're awake.

100
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:00,680
Ling'er.

101
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:02,010
Ling'er, you're awake.

102
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:06,280
I just took a nap.

103
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:07,880
Why are you all here?

104
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,280
Ling'er.

105
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:13,820
Ling'er, first...

106
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:16,640
Drink some water.

107
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:18,280
Slow down.

108
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,280
Ling'er.

109
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:41,440
Why do you look so pale?

110
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:44,520
Go to the Spirit Spring to recuperate quickly.

111
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:45,840
Okay.

112
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:49,280
Take good care of Ling'er for me.

113
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:54,240
Ling'er.

114
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,480
Sister Qingluan.

115
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:56,760
Diyun.

116
00:07:57,760 --> 00:07:59,290
How long have I been asleep?

117
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:01,010
What exactly happened?

118
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:03,480
Nothing happened.

119
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:05,440
You didn't sleep long.

120
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:08,960
Diyun, you tell me.

121
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:12,000
Ling'er, you really didn't sleep long.

122
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:15,440
Diyun, if you don't tell me,

123
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:18,120
then we shall never meet again.

124
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,050
Ling'er, don't.

125
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:22,440
Everything has indeed been resolved.

126
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:23,240
I...

127
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:25,440
Let me explain.

128
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:26,880
Ling'er.

129
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:28,360
For the past three months,

130
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,620
you have been in a coma.

131
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:32,570
We tried everything but couldn't wake you up.

132
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:34,640
Later, my sworn brother found the Grand Shaman,

133
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:36,880
and Diyun brought Lord Yanxi here.

134
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:38,940
Only then were we able to wake you.

135
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,640
I slept for over three months?

136
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:43,799
Thank you for your trouble, Lord Yanxi.

137
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,800
You are too polite, Princess.

138
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:48,200
I didn't do anything.

139
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:50,000
It was all thanks to King Kunmi.

140
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:54,400
Diyun.

141
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:56,280
These are snacks made just this morning.

142
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:57,080
Try some.

143
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:01,360
Mmm, delicious.

144
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:03,760
Sister Qingluan.

145
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:05,240
I don't know why,

146
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:07,160
but I can't use my spiritual power again.

147
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:08,890
You can't use spiritual power?

148
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:11,480
I have no spiritual power in my body now,

149
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:12,680
and I don't know why.

150
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,400
Lord Yanxi.

151
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,800
Please examine Ling'er again quickly.

152
00:09:15,800 --> 00:09:18,640
Is the curse not fully broken yet?

153
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:31,880
Rest assured, everyone.

154
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:34,080
The Huangquan Biluo has been completely neutralized.

155
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,960
The Princess has no spiritual power right now.

156
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:39,480
It is because she has not yet fully absorbed the Seven-Colored Stone.

157
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:41,810
Once her body fully merges with the Stone,

158
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:42,480
by then,

159
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:44,680
the Princess will be able to reshape her true form.

160
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:46,840
Not only will her spiritual power recover,

161
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:49,570
but she will also gain unexpected great fortune.

162
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:51,240
That is good.

163
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,280
That is good.

164
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:53,160
However...

165
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:55,880
However what?

166
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:58,280
Can't you finish your sentence all at once?

167
00:09:58,280 --> 00:09:59,560
What happened?

168
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:00,240
Yunyuan.

169
00:10:01,680 --> 00:10:02,480
Ling'er.

170
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:03,880
What's wrong?

171
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:05,280
I'm fine.

172
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:07,000
We were just discussing my lack of spiritual power.

173
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:08,860
Lord Yanxi is explaining it to us.

174
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:13,880
Please explain in detail, Lord Yanxi.

175
00:10:20,160 --> 00:10:22,880
The Seven-Colored Spirit Bead is a treasure from the Primordial War,

176
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:24,680
left by the Ancestral Dragon upon his death.

177
00:10:24,680 --> 00:10:26,840
The Seven-Colored Stone made from this bead

178
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:29,800
surely does more than merely reshape a physical body.

179
00:10:29,800 --> 00:10:32,880
It is rumored that a body reshaped by the Stone

180
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:34,680
can transform into a supreme spiritual body.

181
00:10:34,680 --> 00:10:36,960
If empowered by a mighty being,

182
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:38,880
not only can the body be reshaped,

183
00:10:38,880 --> 00:10:41,340
but there will be unexpected great fortune.

184
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:47,400
However, the Princess is of the Dragon Clan.

185
00:10:47,400 --> 00:10:48,680
Her true form is powerful.

186
00:10:48,680 --> 00:10:51,880
Although the Seven-Colored Stone has reshaped her body,

187
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:54,560
she still needs to find the Dragon Gate.

188
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:56,760
Only by passing through the trials of the Dragon Gate

189
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:58,600
can she restore her true dragon form.

190
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,530
The Dragon Gate?

191
00:10:59,680 --> 00:11:00,480
What is the Dragon Gate?

192
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:02,200
Why have I never seen any information

193
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:04,260
about the Dragon Gate in any records?

194
00:11:04,280 --> 00:11:06,680
Legend has it that the Dragon Gate has no form.

195
00:11:06,680 --> 00:11:08,040
It is nowhere to be found.

196
00:11:08,040 --> 00:11:10,680
It is not surprising that Your Highness does not know.

197
00:11:10,680 --> 00:11:12,640
What do you mean 'nowhere to be found'?

198
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:15,400
It is said that this Dragon Gate exists beyond the Three Realms

199
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:16,760
and outside the Five Elements.

200
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:18,640
Unless it reveals itself,

201
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,880
no one can find it.

202
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:23,760
Then when did the Dragon Gate last appear?

203
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:26,200
I do not know.

204
00:11:26,400 --> 00:11:27,330
I have only heard

205
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:31,160
that the Dragon Gate is a great opportunity left by the Ancestral Dragon for future generations.

206
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:34,480
Only destined ones of a certain realm can find it.

207
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:35,540
A destined one?

208
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:38,080
What defines a destined one?

209
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,180
Your Highness,

210
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:41,480
I truly do not know.

211
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:55,440
I've cultivated for so long,

212
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:56,900
yet I've made no progress.

213
00:11:58,160 --> 00:12:00,360
How on earth can I find the Dragon Gate?

214
00:12:03,880 --> 00:12:05,960
Ling'er, don't be anxious.

215
00:12:06,680 --> 00:12:08,040
Haste makes waste.

216
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:09,800
I'm not anxious.

217
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:14,280
I just feel that I am weak, pitiful, and helpless right now.

218
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:17,040
I'm always being bullied by you.

219
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:19,560
You, bullied by me?

220
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:24,960
Ling'er.

221
00:12:25,560 --> 00:12:27,040
If you say that,

222
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:29,040
then I am truly wronged.

223
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:33,400
Are you sure it's not me being bullied by you?

224
00:12:35,040 --> 00:12:36,480
How can you be like this?

225
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,480
Be like what?

226
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:42,800
Oh...

227
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:45,160
You are really so bad.

228
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:48,360
If I am so bad,

229
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:51,880
then... do you like it?

230
00:12:52,880 --> 00:12:53,880
You know...

231
00:12:58,560 --> 00:12:59,760
If you don't say it...

232
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:02,040
I'll take it that you like it.

233
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:04,680
Hey, be serious.

234
00:13:04,880 --> 00:13:05,680
Okay.

235
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:07,860
I'll be serious, then.

236
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,640
Since I was born,

237
00:13:19,320 --> 00:13:20,760
you have been by my side,

238
00:13:21,160 --> 00:13:22,820
protecting me time and again.

239
00:13:22,880 --> 00:13:24,480
And now, to save me,

240
00:13:24,560 --> 00:13:26,680
you were willing to be refined into the Seven-Colored Stone.

241
00:13:26,680 --> 00:13:27,440
Thank you.

242
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:29,000
For always being with me,

243
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:40,010
Yunyuan.

244
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:42,040
Now that Linger has lost all her spiritual power,

245
00:13:42,040 --> 00:13:43,120
your cultivation in the future

246
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:44,640
will likely stagnate.

247
00:13:45,560 --> 00:13:47,090
As long as I can save Linger,

248
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:50,020
what does it matter if I lose all my cultivation?

249
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:01,280
Brother.

250
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:04,240
Brother.

251
00:14:04,280 --> 00:14:04,960
All over Kunmi,

252
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:06,880
the Demon Tribe has been harassing the people.

253
00:14:06,880 --> 00:14:07,800
You and Yueying,

254
00:14:07,800 --> 00:14:09,320
take the guards and go rescue them immediately.

255
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:09,840
Okay.

256
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,240
Yunyuan.

257
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:21,880
Go.

258
00:14:26,400 --> 00:14:27,960
But you are all alone.

259
00:14:28,400 --> 00:14:29,660
I'm worried about you.

260
00:14:30,040 --> 00:14:31,440
You are the King of Kunmi.

261
00:14:31,880 --> 00:14:33,680
Protecting Kunmi is your duty.

262
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:34,880
Go.

263
00:14:38,400 --> 00:14:39,680
I will stay right here.

264
00:14:39,680 --> 00:14:40,640
I won't go anywhere.

265
00:14:40,640 --> 00:14:42,100
I'll wait for your return.

266
00:14:46,880 --> 00:14:47,800
Linger,

267
00:14:48,120 --> 00:14:48,880
promise me.

268
00:14:49,560 --> 00:14:51,680
Stay obediently at Yunshenbuzhichu.

269
00:14:51,680 --> 00:14:52,740
Don't go anywhere.

270
00:14:53,680 --> 00:14:54,480
Okay.

271
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:23,680
Why am I now

272
00:15:25,760 --> 00:15:28,440
not even qualified to fight alongside Yunyuan?

273
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:40,680
I want to fight by Yunyuan's side.

274
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:43,960
I want to protect the people of Kunmi even more.

275
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:49,160
Who can help me?

276
00:15:50,480 --> 00:15:53,240
Who can help me?

277
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:24,640
How careless

278
00:16:24,640 --> 00:16:25,960
to turn your back on the enemy.

279
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:27,160
Because you're here.

280
00:16:50,520 --> 00:16:51,120
Qingluan,

281
00:16:51,520 --> 00:16:53,840
return to Yunshenbuzhichu immediately to protect Linger.

282
00:16:53,840 --> 00:16:54,500
I'm worried

283
00:16:54,640 --> 00:16:56,770
this is a diversion by the Demon Tribe.

284
